Aethelgrad Reciprocal Public Code Covenant (ARPCC)
Version 2.6
Effective Date: June 1, 2026

================================================================================
  ARPCC v2.6 – A SOVEREIGN SOURCE-AVAILABLE ENTERPRISE LICENSE
  ================================================================================
  Permissions:   ✓ Commercial use (tiered)  ✓ Modification   ✓ Distribution
  Conditions:    ⚠ 40‑day evaluation for corps  ⚠ AI training restricted  ⚠ No name squatting
                 ⚠ Share‑alike for core changes  ⚠ Attribution
  Enforcement:   🔴 2x standard fee + public disclosure + revocation for cause
================================================================================

TL;DR SUMMARY (UNOFFICIAL):
This Covenant grants free, perpetual use to individuals and hobbyists, but requires commercial entities with over $100,000 USD in annual revenue to purchase a commercial license after a 40-day evaluation. Unlicensed AI training is prohibited and subject to damages. Unlicensed commercial use triggers liquidated damages.

